IN RE Resignation of BROWN. 2017-1669 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 17, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

Sua sponte, Christi Lee Brown, Attorney Registration No. 0062696, last known business address in Lima, Ohio, found in contempt for failure to surrender certificate of admission and file affidavit of compliance on or before March 5, 2018.
